{"tid":2276990,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"柴灣公屋｜神奇屋邨五座樓相連似迷宮 一層近百單位 樓層交錯8樓變16樓考起外賣仔","createTime":"2020-11-08T07:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T15:41:18.000Z","uid":271829,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"358e08a1b159af3015b45f62566f22e36529737e","tid":2276990,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NYWNe5iuqGlYi0Cl4gKCcZQ6gDA=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N5XIRB5LLRGQ7GOWZTTDH4CPS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNYWNe5iuqGlYi0Cl4gKCcZQ6gDA%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN5XIRB5LLRGQ7GOWZTTDH4CPS4.jpg&h=5b7bd352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾多次送餐到興華二邨的外賣員David，幾乎每次都要出動GPS尋找目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KKrdAp_iRAoymNwb9C2gbWeaJFE=/1600x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JJA4BTKKYRHMXAUUS45NWWEAZQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKKrdAp_iRAoymNwb9C2gbWeaJFE%3D%2F1600x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJJA4BTKKYRHMXAUUS45NWWEAZQ.jpeg&h=75c0157e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵盛西邨的空中走廊。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n早前在社交平台有外賣員出帖，指自己去了一個「神奇屋邨」，明明進入了A座，但走了一陣子，發現自己去了B座，再走多幾走，又驚覺自己身處C座，找來找去都找不到送餐的單位，還有很多人留言說試過一樣經歷，難道&hellip;&hellip;他們都去了結界？<br />\n<br />\n其實這條「神奇屋邨」是柴灣興華二邨，在七十年代落成，是由前徙置事務處策劃興建的第七型徙置大廈，全香港只剩下這條屋邨是該設計。全邨共有七座，因為依山而建，特色就是其中五座（展興樓、寧興樓、和興樓、豐興樓及安興樓）相連，只要入了其中一座，就可以互通去其餘四座的不同層數，而剩餘的兩座（樂興樓和裕興樓）亦是互通。由於每座位處的地勢水平不同，所以當你站在平台，其實也正等於身處不同座數的不同樓層，即安興樓及展興樓的八樓、寧興樓及和興樓的四樓、以及豐興樓的十六樓。如果第一次到訪，或會覺得頭暈，記者訪問前特地去走一趟，也迷了好幾次路才稍微弄清楚。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201109/R4XXNX25TZHQ3PEGEIRGTZCXH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201109%2FR4XXNX25TZHQ3PEGEIRGTZCXH4%2F&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft29MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=6fc454d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20201109%2FR4XXNX25TZHQ3PEGEIRGTZCXH4%2F&h=68e788de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20201109/R4XXNX25TZHQ3PEGEIRGTZCXH4/</a>"},{"pid":"7db5215a7506b4e17e4d86234095d26a51338f15","tid":2276990,"uid":24306,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前成日起果度玩捉迷藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f7157c990ab4559704ed86a2cc4a81722a8e5e","tid":2276990,"uid":43369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"勁多廢佬<br />\n低端人口集中地"},{"pid":"834c994a92c574b3ebabe32fd227be9c1b4cf760","tid":2276990,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8f7157c990ab4559704ed86a2cc4a81722a8e5e","tid":2276990,"uid":43369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"勁多廢佬<br />\n低端人口集中地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:31:21.000Z","msg":"宜家就係<br />\n<br />\n廿幾年前好多拳王架"},{"pid":"47f13fceca20ca2a7d108ba6a3225a2f145ccb92","tid":2276990,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"興華邨其實幾特別。"},{"pid":"d7570f5293fb8b30a3ece4b30fb4f92679a5ec4a","tid":2276990,"uid":79793,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:36:28.000Z","msg":"呢到仲有間極深黃茶餐廳，就算知道係廢老邨<br />\n寧願唔要客都要表態，老闆娘仲好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0477e23fa3ece4f9653b50629122172473a1d976","tid":2276990,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"半山公屋<